{"tid":383220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"署理運輸署長李萃珍明日起停任署長一職","createTime":"2017-09-01T10:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T02:53:00.000Z","uid":55981,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4497d8d031f13c476cd40b1f03dcbec05a746f5c","tid":383220,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:06:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://tw.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170821/photo/bkn-20170821125323213-0821_00822_001_04p.jpg?20170821210141\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170821%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170821125323213-0821_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20170821210141&h=83e1e46f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府今日（9月1日）在憲報宣布，署理運輸署長李萃珍明日（9月2日）起停任署長一職。 李萃珍原為運輸署副署長，原署長升遷後，署任署長。李萃珍停止署任後，運輸署長由署理首席政府工程師鄧偉亮署任。 青嶼幹線上月起實施雙向收費，惟收費亭未全面使用配合，導致交通極其擠塞，李萃珍當時與運輸及房屋局局長陳帆到場視察，並向市民致歉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/09-01-2017/41293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F09-01-2017%2F41293&d=rMgaN5TqaeNk4%2FQu35GHkG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=7b71386f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/09-01-2017/41293</a>"},{"pid":"c945fb77ee67d448c27a27b5389181be0766b554","tid":383220,"uid":29464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:07:47.000Z","msg":"本身有得升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91807a30c621abc88157b7934092843e5ddb1c13","tid":383220,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de81867abca3acf382792cd5c52f86ff573d8d42","tid":383220,"uid":103237,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T10:17:18.000Z","msg":"運輸署長由署理首席政府工程師鄧偉亮署任。<br />\n<br />\n聽人講仲仆街"},{"pid":"6144d39df08d6c1faecc233b79078663fd6c3b94","tid":383220,"uid":609